column5: Can anyone recommend a good bait shop in Dryden to pick up our liscense and some leeches? We will be traveling through that area on Saturday the 14th, heading to Lac Seul. As always, appreciate any help.
go to the shell gas station as you go thru town, vert nice people to work with, lostly young ladies, heyanie
Riverside bait 807-223-2113. I called them this AM. Leeches $28C per lb. They will hold them for you.
Thanks for the replys. Uh, Anie, I have to ask - lostly young ladies?
they are alot of fun, hey
